---
---

<div class="overlay-stage" aria-label="Визуальный пример Windows overlay offerGO">
  <div class="screen-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="call-window glass">
    <div class="call-topline">
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <span></span>
      <strong>Live call</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="speaker-lines">
      <i></i>
      <i></i>
      <i></i>
      <i></i>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="offergo-bar glass">
    <strong>offerGO</strong>
    <button type="button">Стоп</button>
    <div class="signal">
      <span class="bar b1"></span>
      <span class="bar b2"></span>
      <span class="bar b3"></span>
      <small>72%</small>
    </div>
    <button type="button" class="ghost">Ответ AI</button>
    <button type="button" class="ghost">Скриншот</button>
  </div>

  <div class="answer-panel glass">
    <div class="answer-meta">
      <span>Думаю...</span>
      <small>live streaming</small>
    </div>
    <p>
      Начните с короткого определения, затем покажите практический пример. Если вопрос про архитектуру,
      назовите trade-off и способ проверки решения.
    </p>
    <div class="prompt-row">
      <span>Короткий запрос</span>
      <strong>Умная модель</strong>
      <strong>Авто</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .overlay-stage {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 560px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(14, 20, 32, 0.86), rgba(3, 5, 10, 0.72));
  }

  .screen-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 46px 46px;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 40%, black, transparent 72%);
  }

  .call-window {
    position: absolute;
    left: 8%;
    right: 8%;
    top: 14%;
    min-height: 250px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 22px;
    opacity: 0.86;
  }

  .call-topline {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .call-topline span {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .call-topline strong {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .speaker-lines {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 50px;
  }

  .speaker-lines i {
    display: block;
    height: 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.1), rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2), rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.04));
  }

  .speaker-lines i:nth-child(1) {
    width: 72%;
  }

  .speaker-lines i:nth-child(2) {
    width: 54%;
  }

  .speaker-lines i:nth-child(3) {
    width: 80%;
  }

  .speaker-lines i:nth-child(4) {
    width: 44%;
  }

  .offergo-bar {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 46px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    width: min(92%, 548px);
    padding: 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    animation: float-bar 5s var(--ease) infinite;
  }

  .offergo-bar strong {
    margin-right: 4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-family: "Space Grotesk", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
  }

  .offergo-bar button {
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
    color: #fff;
    padding: 9px 12px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .offergo-bar .ghost {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .signal {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: end;
    gap: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
  }

  .bar {
    width: 4px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--accent);
    animation: pulse-bar 1s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .b1 {
    height: 11px;
  }

  .b2 {
    height: 17px;
    animation-delay: 120ms;
  }

  .b3 {
    height: 23px;
    animation-delay: 240ms;
  }

  .signal small {
    margin-left: 4px;
    color: var(--soft);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .answer-panel {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    bottom: 46px;
    width: min(88%, 490px);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 18px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .answer-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .answer-meta small {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .answer-panel p {
    margin: 14px 0 18px;
    color: var(--soft);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .prompt-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .prompt-row span,
  .prompt-row strong {
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.055);
    padding: 9px 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .prompt-row span {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .prompt-row strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  @keyframes pulse-bar {
    50% {
      transform: scaleY(0.62);
      opacity: 0.65;
    }
  }

  @keyframes float-bar {
    50% {
      transform: translate(-50%, 8px);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 620px) {
    .overlay-stage {
      min-height: 510px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .offergo-bar {
      top: 28px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .call-window {
      top: 130px;
      min-height: 190px;
    }

    .answer-panel {
      bottom: 24px;
    }

    .prompt-row {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .prompt-row span {
      flex-basis: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
